body_html:
I ran into a similar problem when I tried to use tensorboard.
First I got the error:

from html5lib.filters.base import Filter
ImportError: No module named 'html5lib.filters.base'

I fixed it by unistalling html5lib via pip and installing version 0.9999.
LinuxMint, Anaconda in a python 3.5 env.
